00:00:00.687 --> 00:00:02.368
-SHESTOVA GODA

00:00:02.948 --> 00:00:04.890
SHMUEL SHRA-

00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:07.420
KAUNAS, LITVA.

00:00:12.533 --> 00:00:15.142
azoy vi mir hobn gearbet in Akmener lager

00:00:15.334 --> 00:00:16.914
iz UNK azoy.

00:00:17.427 --> 00:00:19.972
tsvantsik vagonetkes, vifl ikh gedenk

00:00:19.972 --> 00:00:21.454
onhakn kalkh

00:00:21.612 --> 00:00:23.152
un onlodn kalkh

00:00:23.152 --> 00:00:24.418
un aroystsien.

00:00:24.418 --> 00:00:27.025
nor azoy, di mentshn zaynen geven ⟨oyf ⟩ azoy fil shvakh

00:00:27.025 --> 00:00:29.334
az eyn vagonetke gevegn umgefer a ton

00:00:29.526 --> 00:00:30.223
flegn

00:00:30.223 --> 00:00:33.468
fun tsvelf biz fuftsn froyen shtupn di vagonetke.

00:00:33.694 --> 00:00:36.424
froyen, un mir flegn es onlodn di vagonetke.

00:00:36.424 --> 00:00:39.560
ikh umgefer tsen fuftsn mener flegn onlodn di vagonetke.

00:00:39.870 --> 00:00:42.761
flegn doyern umgefer tsen fuftsn mener flegn a tog tsayt

00:00:42.761 --> 00:00:46.364
azoy vi bay a hundert fuftsik mener iz geven, a hundert fuftsik froyen iz geven.

00:00:46.364 --> 00:00:47.258
s'iz umgefer

00:00:47.258 --> 00:00:50.338
tsvelf fuftsn brigades iz geven. azoy vi me hot undz gerufn brigade

00:00:50.338 --> 00:00:53.248
flegn mir koym makhn di norme. oyb me fleg nit makhn di norme

00:00:53.248 --> 00:00:54.158
flegn mir afile

00:00:54.158 --> 00:00:56.798
nit krign di tsvey hundert gram broyt vos iz ⟨undz⟩ geven bashtetikt.

00:00:56.798 --> 00:00:57.940
dos hot men gemuzt makhn.

00:00:57.940 --> 00:00:59.130
ershtns. tsveytns

00:00:59.130 --> 00:01:01.281
fleg kumen tsu geyn der zelber MARCINKUS

00:01:01.281 --> 00:01:02.291
mit a

00:01:02.398 --> 00:01:03.539
shtekn

00:01:03.968 --> 00:01:06.442
un gebn azelkhe klep az s'fleg tsebrekhn di hent.

00:01:06.465 --> 00:01:09.010
un er fleg UNK me ken nit aroysgeyn arbetn

00:01:09.010 --> 00:01:10.630
flegt men krign alts nit keyn broyt

00:01:10.630 --> 00:01:11.994
oder me flegt opshisn.

00:01:12.388 --> 00:01:16.081
mit eyn fal iz geven Akmener lager hot opgeshosn i mener i froyen

00:01:16.081 --> 00:01:19.076
UNK dos ⟨oykh⟩ gedenk ikh nit, ken ikh nit zogn far vos zey flegn

00:01:19.076 --> 00:01:22.103
vi zey farshuldikn dos az zey viln nit arbetn. foylers.

00:01:24.049 --> 00:01:26.473
Akmener lager hot zikh gefunen

00:01:26.800 --> 00:01:27.750
tsvishn

00:01:27.750 --> 00:01:29.493
tsivil bafelker in dorf.

00:01:29.635 --> 00:01:31.080
flegt nokh der arbet

00:01:31.103 --> 00:01:32.211
geshen mir

00:01:32.571 --> 00:01:34.168
undz hobn gehit ukrayner.

00:01:34.377 --> 00:01:37.450
KRAVCHENKO, SAVCHENKO, di ge- familye gedenk ikh

00:01:37.450 --> 00:01:40.280
dos zaynen geven normale mentshn, nor eyner iz geven a UNK familye

00:01:40.280 --> 00:01:42.810
un der iz geven a gazlen. fun gazlonim a gazlen.

00:01:43.017 --> 00:01:45.629
er flegt trogn oyf eyn hant dem biks, eyn hant dem shtekn.

00:01:45.629 --> 00:01:48.683
UNK zayn flikht iz geven nor UNK mir zoln nit antloyfn

00:01:48.683 --> 00:01:51.586
tsum ba- vi mir arbetn iz zayn flikht UNK geven nor nit kukn az dos

00:01:51.586 --> 00:01:53.056
er fleg geyn tsvishn di arbeter

00:01:53.056 --> 00:01:54.740
un ⟨du arbetst⟩ shlekht.

00:01:55.335 --> 00:01:58.504
un flegt men aroys⟨loyfn⟩ fun dort betn a shtikl broyt oder a por bulbes

00:01:58.504 --> 00:02:00.004
kartofl UNK

00:02:00.043 --> 00:02:02.723
flegn andere mentshn gebn. ver fleg gebn, ver fleg nit gebn

00:02:02.723 --> 00:02:05.640
nor vos me fleg darfn farbaygeyn dem heyfl farbaygeyn

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:07.917
vu es hot gelebt dem komandant's

00:02:08.869 --> 00:02:10.128
lyubovnitse.

00:02:10.371 --> 00:02:11.917
⟨mit vemen⟩ er flirtirt.

00:02:11.957 --> 00:02:14.904
fleg es aroyflozn di hint, un di hint flegn tseraysn.

00:02:15.400 --> 00:02:18.991
demolt tor ikh nit fargesn, un ikh muz ibergebn far kinder kinder

00:02:18.991 --> 00:02:21.670
UNK aroyfgelozn di hint, tsvey velf, ⟨azelkhe⟩ velf hint

00:02:21.728 --> 00:02:25.195
tserisn mayn mame's kleyd un tserisn mayn mamen ker- dem kerper

00:02:25.195 --> 00:02:27.155
az fun ir iz gerunen blut vi vaser.

00:02:27.195 --> 00:02:28.859
fun mayn mamen, olevasholem.

00:02:29.288 --> 00:02:31.340
keyn meditsin hobn mir keyne nit gehat.

00:02:31.363 --> 00:02:34.070
mit vos zikh far- ibertsubindn oder bashmirn

00:02:34.070 --> 00:02:35.160
keyn zakh nit geven.

00:02:35.160 --> 00:02:36.473
nor kalte vaser.

00:02:36.473 --> 00:02:40.850
un UNK geton fun zikh, az zi iz gekumen tsu im mit a UNK kleyd, mitn naketn kerper

00:02:40.850 --> 00:02:42.270
un zi iz zikh aroys

00:02:42.270 --> 00:02:42.970
oyfn

00:02:42.970 --> 00:02:46.033
baym shtub un geshtanen di hent ⟨farleytert⟩ azoy

00:02:46.033 --> 00:02:47.240
un azoy gelakht

00:02:47.240 --> 00:02:49.070
un azoy gefreyt zikh vi di hint raysn

00:02:49.070 --> 00:02:50.010
mayn maminken.

00:02:50.162 --> 00:02:52.130
az ikh hob gegebn zikh a shvue

00:02:52.153 --> 00:02:54.020
az ikh muz nemen nekome

00:02:54.448 --> 00:02:55.994
oyb ikh vel nor blaybn lebn.

00:02:56.288 --> 00:02:57.972
dos hob ikh zikh farshprokhn.

00:02:57.972 --> 00:03:00.568
un dem flikht hob ikh oysgefilt. dos iz shpeter.

00:03:03.358 --> 00:03:04.810
ot azoy zenen mir g-

00:03:04.810 --> 00:03:08.870
UNK ⟨s'iz gegangen a tsayt⟩ UNK Akmener lager hobn mir gearbet tsen sho umgefer flegt men arbetn.

00:03:08.870 --> 00:03:11.148
zuntik tsi m'hot gearbet nit gedenk ikh nit

00:03:11.222 --> 00:03:12.248
ken ikh nit zogn.

00:03:12.248 --> 00:03:13.950
UNK ⟨hot men⟩ gearbet gor ale teg.

00:03:14.293 --> 00:03:15.266
UNK

00:03:16.858 --> 00:03:18.910
zayendik in lager hobn mir dervust

00:03:18.910 --> 00:03:22.510
az m'hot aroysgefirt fun Shavl di yidishe kinder mit di eltere mentshn.

00:03:22.510 --> 00:03:24.529
nor genoy vi UNK gevust azoy

00:03:24.529 --> 00:03:26.709
vegn mayn bruder's dray kinderlekh

00:03:26.899 --> 00:03:29.289
un mayn shvegerin's mamen mitn tatn

00:03:29.346 --> 00:03:31.478
hobn mir dervust dan ven mir zaynen gekumen in lager.

00:03:31.478 --> 00:03:33.477
az ⟨m'hot zikh⟩ aroysgefirt alemen

00:03:33.477 --> 00:03:34.081
un

00:03:34.105 --> 00:03:37.341
un m'hot zey avekgefirt in AUSCHWITZ oyf vifl ikh veys fun derayn

00:03:37.341 --> 00:03:40.090
vayl in AUSCHWITZ iz geven gebrakht mayn shvegerin Mere

00:03:40.090 --> 00:03:41.200
fun Rumenye

00:03:41.226 --> 00:03:44.480
hot zi gezogt az for zey iz geven gebrakht litvishe

00:03:44.480 --> 00:03:46.091
yidishe kinder mit froyen

00:03:46.091 --> 00:03:47.391
in AUSCHWITZER lager

00:03:47.391 --> 00:03:48.640
hot men zey farnikht

00:03:48.640 --> 00:03:51.716
un azoy meynen mir az m'hot zey farnikht in AUSCHWITZER lager

00:03:53.055 --> 00:03:54.348
undzer familye.

00:03:56.380 --> 00:03:58.081
dem tsentn DEKABR

00:03:58.081 --> 00:04:00.710
in toyznt nayn hundert dray un fertsikstn yor

00:04:00.868 --> 00:04:03.123
hot undz nit aroysgelozn oyf der arbet.

00:04:03.501 --> 00:04:05.823
m'hot undz arumgeringlt mit koyln varfer.

00:04:07.399 --> 00:04:09.114
der zelber MARCINKUS

00:04:09.222 --> 00:04:11.156
iz arayn in froyen barak

00:04:11.247 --> 00:04:13.378
un er hot far di hentelekh, far di fiselekh

00:04:13.378 --> 00:04:16.573
aroysgeshlept tsen kinder mit an alte froy.

00:04:17.220 --> 00:04:18.001
er

00:04:18.001 --> 00:04:20.482
un vayzt oys hobn nokh ver geholfn fun di ukrayner

00:04:20.482 --> 00:04:21.950
un m'hot zey oysgeshosn.

00:04:21.950 --> 00:04:24.060
ale in eyn, tsunoyfgevorfn in eyn ⟨grube⟩.

00:04:24.060 --> 00:04:24.824
kinder.

00:04:25.270 --> 00:04:28.774
mir hobn gehert klor di geshreyen un klor dem shisn.

00:04:29.117 --> 00:04:31.696
UNK itster shist ⟨men oys⟩ di froyen mit di kinder

00:04:31.696 --> 00:04:36.823
vayl der front hot zikh genentert, hot men shoyn geredt oyf ⟨ver⟩ shpeter undz fun danet aroysfirn, oder m'vet undz farnikhtn.

00:04:37.032 --> 00:04:39.608
dos iz geven ende DEKABR dray un fertsik hob ikh gezogt.

00:04:40.828 --> 00:04:43.154
nakher iz er arayn in lager shikerlekh

00:04:43.154 --> 00:04:44.923
mit a gumene shtekn

00:04:45.418 --> 00:04:48.955
un ikh bin geshtanen grade baym tir. ikh bin geven gegreyt im ontsufaln

00:04:49.047 --> 00:04:50.399
ikh hob bashlosn azoy.

00:04:50.399 --> 00:04:53.349
oyb zey ge- fangen on traybn shisn, UNK onfangen traybn

00:04:53.349 --> 00:04:56.249
mir hobn UNK keyne gever nit gehat, afile keyn meser hobn mir nit gehat.

00:04:56.249 --> 00:04:57.438
faln mir onet

00:04:57.438 --> 00:04:59.359
vos vet zayn UNK mir veysn

00:04:59.359 --> 00:05:00.809
az undzer goyrl iz di grub.

00:05:00.809 --> 00:05:02.307
iz eyder tsu geyn in grub

00:05:02.307 --> 00:05:05.325
on a vidershtand veln mir geyn in grub mit a vidershtand.

00:05:06.597 --> 00:05:09.707
mir zaynen geven a sakh yunge zaynen mir geven in dem undzer mener barak.

00:05:09.707 --> 00:05:10.387
UNK

00:05:10.680 --> 00:05:11.968
UNK ⟨un er vayzt⟩

00:05:11.968 --> 00:05:14.457
tsu mir, mir oyfn hant mitn finger vayzt er

00:05:14.457 --> 00:05:16.406
un nokh etlekhe yunge yinglekh

00:05:16.406 --> 00:05:17.947
nemt di shpates

00:05:18.409 --> 00:05:21.474
un geyt avek dortn un dortn, un fargrobt di kinder.

00:05:22.408 --> 00:05:24.168
undz hobn bagreyt vider tsvey

00:05:24.168 --> 00:05:26.267
bavofnte shoymrim

00:05:26.796 --> 00:05:28.759
mir gekumen, hobn mir gefunen dem ⟨troyerdikn⟩ bild

00:05:28.759 --> 00:05:31.869
lign tsen kinderlekh eyner oyfn tsveytn, shoyn ⟨oyf⟩gevorfene

00:05:32.263 --> 00:05:33.522
nokh vareme

00:05:34.255 --> 00:05:35.087
UNK

00:05:35.087 --> 00:05:37.416
⟨hot men aroysgevizn⟩ a grub lebn froyen lager

00:05:37.416 --> 00:05:40.616
un dortn veln mir zey bagrobn ale tsen kinderlekh mit di

00:05:40.853 --> 00:05:42.079
alte froy.

00:05:42.726 --> 00:05:44.393
un m'hot gezogt a kadesh

