oyb ikh hob nit keyn ⟨toes⟩ in familye.

00:06:01.508 --> 00:06:03.240
mir zaynen gekumen kerik in lager.

00:06:03.313 --> 00:06:05.484
oyf morgn kerik oyf avek oyf der arbet.

00:06:05.912 --> 00:06:07.258
un azoy hobn mir gearbet

00:06:07.258 --> 00:06:10.023
bizn umgefer mart fir un fertsikstn.

00:06:10.890 --> 00:06:12.672
az zikh ongefangen der groyser

00:06:13.017 --> 00:06:13.984
shlakht

