me UNK me klapt on in tir. es geyen araynet

00:18:48.180 --> 00:18:50.749
etlekhe militer layt sovetishe

00:18:50.940 --> 00:18:55.085
un me git di hent, vos dem ershtn mol far fir yor tsayt hot men mir derlangt a hant.

00:18:55.227 --> 00:18:56.734
zayt ikh bin geven in geto

00:18:56.734 --> 00:18:57.780
un in lager

00:18:57.780 --> 00:18:59.661
hot keyner keyn hant undz nit gegebn.

00:18:59.661 --> 00:19:01.093
nit geven, zey hobn nit gevust

00:19:01.093 --> 00:19:03.323
vos zey hobn derlangt di hant, ⟨hobn zey zikh⟩ bagrist mit alemen

00:19:03.323 --> 00:19:05.243
un zey hobn UNK oysgeton di hitl un dokh avekgezetst

00:19:05.243 --> 00:19:06.881
ongefangen reydn dertseyln

00:19:07.039 --> 00:19:08.419
mentshn vi mentshn.

00:19:08.419 --> 00:19:10.740
ikh shpir shoyn UNK az ikh bin a mentsh kerik vi

00:19:10.740 --> 00:19:12.300
ikh bin aza mentshn vi ale mentshn

00:19:12.300 --> 00:19:13.900
UNK tut mir ⟨vey⟩ a mentsh

00:19:13.900 --> 00:19:15.510
un me git mir di hant vi a mentsh

00:19:15.544 --> 00:19:17.127
un me bagrist zikh mit mir

00:19:17.127 --> 00:19:19.620
un zaynen gezesn a vayle un geredt un aroys UNK antsheydet

00:19:19.620 --> 00:19:20.550
zikh nokhgefregt

00:19:20.550 --> 00:19:22.493
un vider UNK mir gebn di hant aroysgeyendik

00:19:22.493 --> 00:19:24.974
hob ikh zikh nit gegleybt, meyn ikh s'iz a kholem. nit gleybn

00:19:24.974 --> 00:19:26.856
az dos iz d- a realer emes

00:19:26.856 --> 00:19:29.530
az mir UNK kerik gevorn a mentsh mit mentshn glaykh.

00:19:29.530 --> 00:19:31.110
vayle UNK bin geven in geto

00:19:31.110 --> 00:19:33.530
hobn mir zikh aleyn shoyn oyfgehert tsu haltn far mentshn

00:19:33.530 --> 00:19:35.070
vayle m'hot undz ⟨zikh⟩ nit gerekhnt.

00:19:35.338 --> 00:19:37.571
der UNK hob ikh gezogt dem ershtn mol UNK

00:19:37.571 --> 00:19:38.981
dershist UNK derhargenen

00:19:38.981 --> 00:19:41.271
UNK vi a shvebl aruntervarfn oyf der erd.

00:19:44.215 --> 00:19:46.178
⟨nakher⟩, gekumen tsu geyn

00:19:46.178 --> 00:19:49.052
nokh zey gekumen an elterer mentsh, oykh a militer layt.

00:19:49.328 --> 00:19:51.516
ikh hob farshtanen az se muz zayn a polkovnik

00:19:52.112 --> 00:19:54.033
un er hot ⟨zikh⟩ avekgezesn, dertseylt

00:19:54.033 --> 00:19:57.203
freg ikh ver vi, ikh hob UNK a bisl UNK rusish geredt etlekhe verter

00:19:57.242 --> 00:19:59.531
zogt er "do zaynen mir sovyetn soldatn

00:20:00.111 --> 00:20:01.370
gekumen do."

00:20:01.377 --> 00:20:04.240
in dem geshprekh reydndik mit zey

00:20:04.482 --> 00:20:05.488
der zeyger

00:20:05.663 --> 00:20:07.867
g- hot gemuzt vern arum nayn tsen.

00:20:08.785 --> 00:20:11.141
ikh her a tuml, a geshrey, me shrayt

00:20:11.164 --> 00:20:14.111
oyfn barg iz ongegangen, ongeforn a daytshishe

00:20:14.539 --> 00:20:15.810
grupe soldatn.

00:20:15.810 --> 00:20:17.581
kh'meyn umgefer zayn arum a batalyon.

00:20:17.581 --> 00:20:18.684
azoy meyn ikh.

00:20:20.277 --> 00:20:25.101
ikh gib a kuk oyfn barg soldatn, zogt der balebos az er git UNK a hant un UNK zogt er

00:20:25.101 --> 00:20:28.231
itster vet men undz farnikhtn. dos zaynen in vald di rusishe armey

00:20:28.231 --> 00:20:30.850
un oyfn barg zaynen di daytshn. UNK

00:20:30.850 --> 00:20:32.680
shisn, un m'vet undz farbrenen.

00:20:32.781 --> 00:20:35.104
dos iz geven a zeyer tragishe zakh in dorf.

00:20:36.021 --> 00:20:39.221
fun vald UNK zey hobn nit gevust di daytshn az der royter armey gefint zikh in vald

00:20:39.221 --> 00:20:41.281
un der royter armey hot nit gevust er darf onkumen.

00:20:41.281 --> 00:20:42.861
zey, zayendik in vald

00:20:42.861 --> 00:20:45.628
hobn zey bamerkt az s'kumt on a daytshishe makhne soldatn

00:20:45.628 --> 00:20:48.614
hobn zey gelozt zey kumen. zey hobn oysgeshpant di ferd

00:20:48.614 --> 00:20:51.641
un zikh ongefangen dortn vashn, greytn esn.

00:20:51.951 --> 00:20:55.339
iz aroys etlekhe tankes fun vald. ikh ken nit zogn genoy, tsvey tsi dray

00:20:55.339 --> 00:20:56.738
un m'hot ongefangen shisn

00:20:56.738 --> 00:20:58.968
in di daytshn. ⟨hot men zey⟩ tsehakt shtiker

00:20:59.055 --> 00:21:01.318
umgefer a hundert fuftsik, tsvey hundert meter

00:21:01.318 --> 00:21:05.088
iz geven shtiker fleysh hot zikh gevelgert fun di ⟨tserisene⟩ daytshishe soldatn.

00:21:08.202 --> 00:21:11.115
ver s'iz antlofn iz antlofn, un ver geblibn geblibn.

00:21:11.948 --> 00:21:13.708
avek a kurtse tsayt

00:21:13.708 --> 00:21:15.873
geyen soldatn iber di shtiber

00:21:16.099 --> 00:21:17.277
un me zogt

00:21:17.277 --> 00:21:20.399
"ale yunge mener mit lopetes, mit shpates

00:21:20.399 --> 00:21:22.253
dortn oyfn barg muzt ir avekgeyn."

00:21:23.727 --> 00:21:25.698
nu, zogt der balebos "nem a shpate

00:21:25.698 --> 00:21:29.022
un gey ⟨adortn⟩." ikh kum tsu geyn UNK. shteyt a militerisher

00:21:29.022 --> 00:21:30.102
a militer man

00:21:30.102 --> 00:21:34.081
a sovyetisher ⟨vos zogt⟩ "⟨do darf men oysgrobn a grub oyf zey bagrobn, di daytshn."

00:21:35.185 --> 00:21:36.177
⟨nu, me flegt⟩

00:21:36.177 --> 00:21:38.782
far mir iz geven, di greste simkhe, ken nit zayn

00:21:38.782 --> 00:21:40.992
mit a tog tsurik volt der zelber daytsh

00:21:40.992 --> 00:21:42.062
in mir geshosn

00:21:42.062 --> 00:21:43.256
⟨oder⟩ vi ⟨er hot⟩ geshosn

00:21:43.256 --> 00:21:44.826
vi nit keyn neytike zakh

00:21:44.826 --> 00:21:47.618
UNK un itster darf ikh im geyn bagrobn. dos iz shoyn di ershte

00:21:47.618 --> 00:21:49.570
di ershte nekome ⟨geven⟩ vos ikh hob derlebt

00:21:49.570 --> 00:21:51.630
nokh genoye fir yor tsayt krig.

00:21:51.672 --> 00:21:53.556
di ershte nekome UNK bagrobn.

00:21:54.625 --> 00:21:55.954
grobndik di grub

00:21:55.954 --> 00:21:58.634
ze ikh s'kumt tsu geyn Shaye Rayz, a Shavler.

00:21:58.894 --> 00:22:01.759
er iz oykh geblibn lebn dort. er hot zikh oysbahaltn UNK bay arumike mentshn.

00:22:01.759 --> 00:22:04.468
mer hob ikh nisht getrofn keyn oysbahaltene in dem gantsn gegnt.

00:22:04.468 --> 00:22:07.038
ikh hob zikh oysbahaltn tsayt UNK, un Shaye Rayz

00:22:07.230 --> 00:22:08.104
getrofn.

00:22:08.104 --> 00:22:09.721
nu, mir hobn zikh derfreyt, tsekusht

00:22:10.521 --> 00:22:13.310
hot men oysgegrobn di grub, shoyn gefodert mir veln zey bagrobn

00:22:13.310 --> 00:22:16.537
un kerik gekumen bay ⟨KEVINSKASn⟩ un ikh hob azoy ⟨ba-⟩ gearbet nokh bay im umgefer

00:22:16.537 --> 00:22:18.407
a akht tsen teg hob ikh bay im gearbet

00:22:18.407 --> 00:22:20.268
vayle Shavl iz geven nokh nit farnumen.

00:22:21.405 --> 00:22:23.940
az ⟨Shavler⟩ hobn dervust az UNK az Shavl iz farnumen

00:22:23.940 --> 00:22:25.500
zog ikh "ikh ker zikh in Shavl."

00:22:25.500 --> 00:22:26.740
zogt er "gey nit.

00:22:26.940 --> 00:22:30.250
Shavl iz umruik. iz do dort farsheydene mentshn loyfn arum un bavofnte

00:22:30.250 --> 00:22:31.630
un m'vet dir derhargenen UNK

00:22:31.630 --> 00:22:34.393
ikh hob im nit gezogt az ikh bin ⟨keyn⟩ yid, un er hot nit gevust az ikh bin ⟨keyn⟩ yid.

00:22:34.450 --> 00:22:35.844
kh'hob keyn zakh nit dermont.

00:22:36.036 --> 00:22:37.464
zog ikh "ikh gey in Shavl."

00:22:37.842 --> 00:22:43.200
iz er zeyer gevorn umtsufridn geblibn. zogt er "do host a groysn feler" zogt er. "du host ⟨do⟩ tsu esn un tsu trinken un tsu shlofn

00:22:43.200 --> 00:22:45.590
un ikh vel dir nokh batsoln az s'vet endikn zikh der zumer

00:22:45.688 --> 00:22:48.140
un vos geystu UNK? m'vet dir bald tsunemen in armey."

00:22:48.140 --> 00:22:50.450
er, der elterer mentsh, hot farshtanen az me nemt in armey

00:22:50.450 --> 00:22:51.430
glaykh farshtanen.

00:22:52.489 --> 00:22:54.643
UNK nit ⟨gekukt⟩ UNK dos hob ikh nit gefolgt.

00:22:55.307 --> 00:22:56.938
ikh bin gekumen in Shavl

00:22:56.944 --> 00:22:58.910
bin ikh opgeven a tog tsvey in Shavl

00:22:58.910 --> 00:23:00.700
hot men oysgegebn a UNK meldungen

00:23:00.700 --> 00:23:02.060
az ale mener

00:23:02.513 --> 00:23:06.962
muzn ⟨vern⟩ muzn kumen zikh meldn in VOENKOMAT oyf mobilizatsye. m'hot shoyn gemoldn mobilizatsye.

00:23:08.993 --> 00:23:12.075
trakht ikh, un ikh hob gehat a gelegnheyt nit tsu geyn in armey.

00:23:12.840 --> 00:23:15.688
zayendik in UNK in LIETUKIS

00:23:15.688 --> 00:23:17.818
ven ikh hob gearbet kumedik fun Akmener lager

00:23:17.886 --> 00:23:20.107
hob ikh gearbet tsaytvaylik oyf a traktor.

00:23:21.565 --> 00:23:23.685
ikh ze me firt dem traktor, me shlept.

00:23:25.075 --> 00:23:28.494
gey ikh tsu tsu ⟨dem VOENNEM⟩, zog ikh "ikh hob oyf dem traktor gearbet."

00:23:28.602 --> 00:23:31.616
zogt er "zeyer gut." git er mir a nem far di hant, zogt er "⟨un⟩ kum.

00:23:32.382 --> 00:23:34.063
mir darfn hobn a traktorist."

00:23:34.896 --> 00:23:38.737
ikh ze vi er firt mir tsu AUSROS nayntsn. dortn iz gevezn N.K.V.D.

00:23:39.013 --> 00:23:41.556
in fertsikst, eyn un fertsikstn yor N.K.V.D. UNK dos iz geven

00:23:41.556 --> 00:23:42.316
shreklekh

00:23:42.316 --> 00:23:43.936
azoy vi GESTAPO bay di daytshn

00:23:43.936 --> 00:23:45.396
azoy geven N.K.V.D.

00:23:45.396 --> 00:23:46.266
geven shreklekh.

00:23:46.266 --> 00:23:48.052
un er firt mir arayn in anshtalt

00:23:48.177 --> 00:23:50.736
un er shtelt mir tsu dortn, zayne

00:23:54.133 --> 00:23:55.376
ye? ⟨yede⟩.

00:23:55.483 --> 00:23:56.861
nu nu, gut, gut.

00:23:57.154 --> 00:23:59.342
meyle, bay zey bin ikh nit geblibn.

00:23:59.415 --> 00:24:02.197
kh'hob getrofn zayendik in, ⟨kh'hob nit gevelt⟩ zayn bay zey dinen

00:24:02.197 --> 00:24:03.907
dokh ikh muz geyn nemen nekome

00:24:03.907 --> 00:24:06.377
far mayne shvester, far mayne brider, far mayne kinder.

00:24:06.377 --> 00:24:09.187
ikh meyn ikh vel do zitsn un ikh fil UNK ⟨azoy⟩ dortn zayn a diner.

00:24:09.187 --> 00:24:10.997
ikh gey oyfn front nemen nekome.

00:24:11.076 --> 00:24:15.120
kh'hob, dan shoyn arayngegangen in Shavl UNK untergang di zekste litvishe divizye.

00:24:15.649 --> 00:24:17.232
geven yidishe soldatn

00:24:17.232 --> 00:24:20.030
vos zaynen gekumen, zogn tsu mir "gey nit

00:24:20.239 --> 00:24:21.880
m'vet endikn di krig on dir.

00:24:21.880 --> 00:24:23.850
bist geblibn lebn fun geto, fun lager

00:24:24.053 --> 00:24:26.308
shtub zikh durkh di tsayt avu nit iz.

00:24:26.702 --> 00:24:29.853
un mir veln shoyn farendikn on dir. ⟨vert⟩ UNK mir" zogt er "hobn nit keyn andere veg.

00:24:29.853 --> 00:24:32.193
vu tsu loyfn, un du torst nit geyn, darfst nit geyn."

00:24:32.200 --> 00:24:33.750
ikh hob zey nisht gefolgt

00:24:33.992 --> 00:24:36.571
un ikh bin avek un gekumen in VOENKOMAT, hob ikh zikh tsugeshtelt

00:24:36.571 --> 00:24:40.331
"gut, bist gekumen" zogt er "gut." un ven ikh hob geven gekumen in N., in N.K.V.D.

00:24:40.331 --> 00:24:41.811
hot er UNK ⟨aroysgegebn⟩ a

00:24:41.811 --> 00:24:44.121
a dokument az in mir ne-

00:24:44.121 --> 00:24:46.461
in mir tor, tor men nit nemen in armey.

00:24:46.461 --> 00:24:48.127
NE PODLEZHET MOBILIZATSYA.

00:24:49.652 --> 00:24:52.788
hot er gezogt ot "far vos geystu az du host aza dokument?" zog ikh "ikh vil UNK frayvilik

00:24:52.788 --> 00:24:53.858
nemen nekome."

00:24:54.006 --> 00:24:55.164
der VOENKOM.

00:24:55.170 --> 00:24:58.408
zogt er "nu, oyber du vilst ⟨azoy⟩" zogt er "nem a ⟨shtikl papir⟩ fun ⟨mikh⟩

00:24:58.408 --> 00:25:00.508
oder shikt mir avek bay UNK farshraybt ir

00:25:00.508 --> 00:25:01.931
un nemt mir shoyn tsu."

00:25:02.494 --> 00:25:06.080
durkhgegangen durkh eyn tir, a tsveyte tir bin ikh shoyn geven a UNK mobilizirter soldat.

00:25:06.080 --> 00:25:07.670
dortn geven a farmakhter geheft

00:25:08.080 --> 00:25:10.048
un dortn hot men tsunoyfgeklibn

00:25:10.932 --> 00:25:12.580
avekgezetst oyf mashines

00:25:12.737 --> 00:25:14.064
un avekgefirt

00:25:14.442 --> 00:25:16.191
in Aleksandrier hoyf.

00:25:17.108 --> 00:25:18.380
dortn iz geven der

00:25:18.380 --> 00:25:20.620
vu me ⟨tsenemt shoyn⟩ ale naye soldatn tsunoyfn.

00:25:20.685 --> 00:25:22.687
dort hot men undz oysgebodn

00:25:22.845 --> 00:25:24.521
oysgesh- opgeshorn

00:25:24.521 --> 00:25:26.130
ibergeton in kleyder

00:25:26.130 --> 00:25:29.380
un dos gedoyert etlekhe teg di protsedur. nisht gevorn azoy shnel.

00:25:30.321 --> 00:25:32.947
⟨hot men undz⟩ umgefer a tsen teg bashult

00:25:32.970 --> 00:25:35.141
un m'hot undz tseteylt shoyn in di teyln.

00:25:35.552 --> 00:25:36.992
ikh bin arayngefaln

00:25:36.992 --> 00:25:40.046
in di zekste divizye geven, tsvey hundert nayn un fertsikstn polk

00:25:40.046 --> 00:25:41.430
drite rote.

00:25:41.430 --> 00:25:45.125
mayn KOMANDIR ROTY iz geven a yidisher bokher fun BIRZAI, Elman.

00:25:45.125 --> 00:25:46.464
leytenant Elman.

00:25:46.892 --> 00:25:48.517
mayn KOMANDIR VZVOD

00:25:48.517 --> 00:25:51.392
iz geven a UNK, leytenant Levin, a Ponevezher.

00:25:52.562 --> 00:25:53.281
UNK

00:25:53.490 --> 00:25:55.006
dos in drite rote zaynen mir geven

00:25:55.006 --> 00:25:57.636
tsu hundert dray mentshn hot men UNK mobilizirt geven

00:25:57.636 --> 00:25:58.856
ongekompletirt

00:25:58.856 --> 00:26:00.866
tsi hundert draysik mentshn gedenk ikh nit.

00:26:00.866 --> 00:26:03.173
un azoy zaynen mir vider shoyn gevorn a soldat

00:26:03.173 --> 00:26:05.330
un dem ershtn shlakht hobn mir ongenumen

00:26:06.045 --> 00:26:06.810
in

00:26:06.810 --> 00:26:08.475
AUGUST monat oder

00:26:08.475 --> 00:26:10.175
ende ⟨yuli oder⟩ onfang AUGUST

00:26:10.185 --> 00:26:12.620
ven der daytsh hot zikh gerisn a tsveytn mol oyf Shavl.

00:26:12.711 --> 00:26:14.648
hob ikh dem ershtn shlakht ongenumen.

00:26:14.648 --> 00:26:15.759
nor do hobn mir keyn

00:26:16.322 --> 00:26:19.792
fal- keyn, mir hobn fun keynem nit farlorn, keyner fun undz nit umgekumen.

00:26:19.832 --> 00:26:21.887
azoy bin ikh shoyn geven a soldat

00:26:21.887 --> 00:26:24.857
bizn ershtn SENTYABR' fir un fertsikstn.

00:26:24.857 --> 00:26:26.975
ershtn SENTYABR' fir un fertsikstn

00:26:26.975 --> 00:26:29.276
zaynen mir avek ongefangen der groyser

00:26:29.434 --> 00:26:31.650
ongrayf oyf Daytshland zaynen mir avek.

00:26:31.650 --> 00:26:32.313
UNK

00:26:33.467 --> 00:26:35.016
dem ershtn SENTYABR'

00:26:35.016 --> 00:26:38.928
fir un fertsik fun divizye hobn mir zikh oyfge⟨UNK⟩ avek ⟨un⟩ tsum shlakht

00:26:39.120 --> 00:26:41.983
zaynen mir aroys hunder- dray- hundert draytsn mentshn.

00:26:42.580 --> 00:26:47.484
ikh bin opgegangen nit vayt KRAZIAI, dos iz a shtetele hinter Kelem, KRAZIAI, a dorf PAKRAZANTIS.

00:26:47.507 --> 00:26:48.176
UNK

00:26:48.267 --> 00:26:50.049
dortn hot men mir farvundet

00:26:50.933 --> 00:26:52.901
un nokh tsvey soldat mit mir.

00:26:53.160 --> 00:26:54.659
forn farvundn

00:26:54.659 --> 00:26:56.310
hot men undz oysgestroyet.

00:26:56.721 --> 00:26:59.240
m'hot undz geshikt brengen esn. azoy hot zikh ongefangen.

00:26:59.240 --> 00:27:01.288
zaynen mir shoyn geblibn finf un tsvantsik

00:27:01.699 --> 00:27:04.418
mitn komandi- mit dem leytenant Elman UNK

00:27:04.418 --> 00:27:06.618
nor mayn KOMANDIR VZVOD hot nokh ⟨oykh⟩ gelebt.

00:27:06.618 --> 00:27:09.456
zogt er azoy UNK. "nem far fuftsik mentshn."

00:27:10.272 --> 00:27:12.951
zenen mir avek brengen esn, un kumendik tsurik mit di esn

00:27:12.951 --> 00:27:14.602
ot dortn hot men mir farvundet.

00:27:15.199 --> 00:27:17.000
nakher ⟨m'hot⟩ farvundet hot mir avekgefirt

00:27:17.000 --> 00:27:19.080
lebn KRAZIAI ⟨der⟩ kleyne shtetele

00:27:19.350 --> 00:27:22.072
Kelmer APSKRITIS KELME UNK

00:27:22.072 --> 00:27:24.963
dortn bin ikh gelegn, a feld BOL'NITSA geven, a

00:27:26.033 --> 00:27:27.840
VOENNE UNK POLEVOY GOSPITAL.

00:27:27.840 --> 00:27:30.450
UNK a feld, a feld BOL'NITSA.

00:27:30.285 --> 00:27:31.831
feld shpitol efsher.

00:27:31.332 --> 00:27:31.902
DA.

00:27:31.902 --> 00:27:32.931
dort hot mir

00:27:32.931 --> 00:27:33.842
oysgeheylt

